data.description: Experience this charming Cottage Bungalow, a perfect haven for first-time home buyers! Indulge in a culinary adventure with SouthPaw Sushi, King Kong Brewing, UpTown Takeout, and Shift Coffee House all within a short walk from your doorstep. Located conveniently a short distance from Downtown, where shopping, entertainment, and cultural experiences await. The energy and excitement of the Golden1 Center is also just moments away, ensuring you never miss a game or concert. Get there by public transportation with no transfers or a quick 10 minute drive. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this little oasis yours. Schedule your showing today and ask about the potentially assumable loan at a 5% interest rate and step into a world where each day is an adventure and the best of the city is right at your fingertips! Great potential to add an ADU on the property as well.
